\c 81
\s Vanhu ngavarumbidze Jehovha, vamutende iye oga
\d Kumutungamiriri wokuimba; neGititi. Pisarema raAsafi.
\p
\v 1 Imbirai Mwari kwazvo, iye simba redu; pururudzai kuna Mwari waJakove.
\v 2 Vambai rwiyo, muridze ngoma, nembira dzinonakidza nomutengeramwa.
\v 3 Ridzai hwamanda pakugara komwedzi, napakuchena komwedzi, pamutambo wedu wakatarwa.
\v 4 Nokuti ndizvo zvakatemerwa zvakarairwa naMwari waJakove.
\v 5 Wakazvitema muna Josefa kuti chive chipupuriro, panguva yaakanorwa nenyika yeIjipiti; pandakanzwa rurimi rwandakange ndisingazivi.
\p
\v 6 Ndakabvisa mutoro pafudzi rake; maoko ake akaregedza dengu.
\v 7 Iwe wakadana pakutambudzika, ndikakurwira; ndakakupindura ndiri panovanda kutinhira; ndakakuidza pamvura zhinji yeMeribha.
\v 8 Inzwai vanhu vangu, ndikupupurirei; haiwa Israeri, dai waida hako kunditeerera!
\v 9 Ngakurege kuvapo pakati penyu mwari wokumwe; musanamata kunomumwe mwari wavatorwa.
\v 10 Ndini Jehovha Mwari wako, akakubudisa panyika yeEgipita; shamisa muromo wako kwazvo, ndigouzadza.
\p
\v 11 Asi vanhu vangu havana kuteerera inzwi rangu; Israeri wakandiramba chose.
\v 12 Saka ndakavaregera paukukutu bwemoyo yavo, kuti vafambe namano avo.
\p
\v 13 Haiwa, dai vanhu vangu vainditeerera havo, dai Israeri aifamba nenzira dzangu!
\v 14 Ndingadai ndakakurumidza kukunda vavengi vavo, nokurova vadzivisi vavo noruoko rwangu.
\v 15 Vanovenga Jehovha vaizviisa pasi pake; asi nguva yavo yaivapo nokusingaperi.
\v 16 Angadai aivadyisawo zviyo zvakaisvonaka; ndaikugutsa nohuchi hunobva padombo.
